Description:
You come to a large stone arch in the middle of the forest, at one side of the arch you see a stall run by a werewolf, when you approach he says:

"Hey, hey, finally some customers! Come close and look at my wares. Half of these items come from the bandits, I'm sure there is something interesting you might need.

Oh... by the way... I didn't kill that boy over there... he was already dead this morning when I came to set up the stall."
DescriptionAction: This may be a good time to do some shopping.
